88)\\n\\n- `content.ExportData` is always nil for OpenCode\\n- Set `ExportData: content.Transcript` instead of `ExportData: content.ExportData`\\n\\n### 4. Remove `export.json` dead code\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/paths/paths.go`**: Remove `ExportDataFileName = \\\"export.json\\\"`\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/checkpoint/temporary.go`**: Remove `GetExportDataFromCommit` function (lines 612-633)\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/checkpoint/committed.go`**:\\n- Remove `export.json` write in `writeSessionFiles` (lines 379-390)\\n- Remove `export.json` read in `ReadSessionContent` (lines 814-819)\\n- Remove `ExportData` from `GetSessionLog` return value (line 992) — update signature to return 3 values instead of 4\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/checkpoint/checkpoint.go`**:\\n- Remove `ExportData` field from `WriteCommittedOptions` (line 281-284)\\n- Remove `ExportData` field from `SessionContent` (line 366-370)\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go`**:\\n- Remove `export.json` reading blocks (lines 429-437 and 481-488)\\n- Remove `ExportData` from `ExtractedSessionData`\\n\\n**`cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_types.go`**: Remove `ExportData` field from `ExtractedSessionData` (line 65)\\n\\n### 5. Update callers of `GetSessionLog` / `LookupSessionLog`\\n\\nAfter removing the `exportData` return value, update all call sites:\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/rewind.go`: `restoreSessionTranscriptFromStrategy`\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/resume.go`: `LookupSessionLog` call\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/checkpoint/committed.go`: `LookupSessionLog` wrapper\\n\\n### 6. Update tests\\n\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/integration_test/agent_test.go` line 1033-1035: Remove the `ExportData` assertion from `ReadSession` test (ExportData on AgentSession is still set by OpenCode's ReadSession — that's fine, it's the WriteSession callers that changed)\\n- Any tests that reference `ExportDataFileName` or `GetExportDataFromCommit`\\n\\n### 7. Keep `ExportData` on `agent.AgentSession`\\n\\nThe `ExportData` field on `AgentSession`