onLog` wrapper\\n\\n### 6. Update tests\\n\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/integration_test/agent_test.go` line 1033-1035: Remove the `ExportData` assertion from `ReadSession` test (ExportData on AgentSession is still set by OpenCode's ReadSession — that's fine, it's the WriteSession callers that changed)\\n- Any tests that reference `ExportDataFileName` or `GetExportDataFromCommit`\\n\\n### 7. Keep `ExportData` on `agent.AgentSession`\\n\\nThe `ExportData` field on `AgentSession` (agent/session.go) is still useful — it's how callers tell `WriteSession()` what to import. OpenCode's `ReadSession` still sets it. Only the checkpoint-level storage of `export.json` is removed.\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n```bash\\nmise run fmt && mise run lint && mise run test:ci\\n```\\n\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"50b93923-0824-467f-9784-aa2c13499111\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli_experiments\",\"sessionId\":\"f5948329-6a47-406a-9742-147b4b94dcfd\",\"version\":\"2.1.47\",\"gitBranch\":\"soph/opencode-refactor\",\"slug\":\"typed-fluttering-harp\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-opus-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_016yVkz8A7ppRStK8uWnKGav\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"\\n\\n\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":14695,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":29846,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":14695},\"output_tokens\":10,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"}},\"requestId\":\"req_011CYKb4zKYZm26Yy61imwF7\",\"type\":\"assistant\",\"uuid\":\"6ffbcaf5-360d-4295-b1d6-18e195c0acb3\",\"timestamp\":\"2026-02-20T15:51:42.071Z\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"6ffbcaf5-360d-4295-b1d6-18e195c0acb3\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/soph/Work/entire/devenv/cli_experiments\",\"sessionId\":\"f5948329-6a47-406a-9742-147b4b94dcfd\",\"version\":\"2.1.47\",\"